name: Reactive Armor
desc: Each time Timbersaw is attacked, he gains increased health regen and armor.

name: Rocket Barrage
desc: Launches a salvo of rockets at nearby enemy units in a radius around the Gyrocopter.  Lasts 3 seconds.

name: Cursed Crown
desc: Dark Willow casts an ancient fae curse on the target. After a delay, the target and nearby enemies are stunned.

name: Dragon Tail
desc: Dragon Knight smites an enemy unit in melee range with his shield, stunning it while dealing minor damage.  When in Elder Dragon Form, the cast range increases to 400.

name: Demonic Purge
desc: Purges the target enemy unit, removing positive buffs, and slowing the target for the duration.  The unit slowly regains its speed until the end of the duration, upon which damage is dealt.  Units under the effect of Disruption can still be affected by Demonic Purge. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter. DISPEL TYPE: Basic Dispel

name: Grow
desc: Tiny gains craggy mass, increases his power and causes him to shrug off debuffs.

name: Primal Split
desc: Splits Brewmaster into elements, forming 3 specialized warriors, adept at survival. If any of them survive until the end of their summoned timer, the Brewmaster is reborn. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.

name: Enfeeble
desc: Weakens an enemy unit, reducing its physical damage.

name: Mist Coil
desc: Abaddon releases a coil of deathly mist that can damage an enemy unit or heal a friendly unit at the cost of some of Abaddon's health.

name: Whirling Death
desc: Timbersaw whirls extremely sharp edges, damaging enemies and destroying trees around him in an area.  If an enemy hero is affected, it loses some of its primary attribute for a short duration.  Whirling Death will deal Pure damage if a tree is cut down in the process.
